data.description: Welcome to this simply adorable 3 bedroom, 1 bath ranch home with beautiful wood floors and lots of natural lighting.  The eat-in kitchen has beautiful wood cabinetry that is ceiling high. The partially finished rec room in the lower level offers additional living space and endless possibilities. The large fenced-in back yard provides privacy and running room for your fur-baby. Don't miss out on this fantastic home in a desirable neighborhood - schedule your showing TODAY!
